{"tid":2126973,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"來吧 ! 大混亂 ! 期待手持午餐肉就有閪屌的日子!!!!!!!!!","createTime":"2020-07-27T06:04:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T02:18:57.000Z","uid":111460,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"550f5ca5be2714c937c6d52b2d94dc0a10a3c7ef","tid":2126973,"uid":111460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:04:42.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎又好，社區爆發又好，721又好，831又好，有咩事發生都唔驚，只要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然，到有日真係出現全香港範圍MAP炮就咩都唔使<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/163932_a2cdc25e37dba43ebb1f73f9ef75e4e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F163932_a2cdc25e37dba43ebb1f73f9ef75e4e1.jpg&h=fc554873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/11/203207_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F203207_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=71add882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n放喺廚房櫃嘅罐頭同米，米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿，到中國午餐肉，回煱肉，豆，菜，金寶湯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3dHRiV5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3dHRiV5.jpg&h=bb698acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一箱箱未開，太多，放到出廳 [依啲全部係魚]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/164003_45a6f56b9383021925f49be7d93c4258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F164003_45a6f56b9383021925f49be7d93c4258.jpg&h=61f1bb56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水污染，未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐，依家啲水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/11/203200_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F11%2F203200_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=84582126&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即食麵 有5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n特大災難~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無嘢買嘅日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待手持午餐肉就可以有閪屌嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd55a5e29a4ce14ae8e6a1f747e53e20e77d5e44","tid":2126973,"uid":263261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:05:52.000Z","msg":"年經<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b980f5c6106c02a39fa751c32e21236f8638526","tid":2126973,"uid":219583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:06:41.000Z","msg":"呢幾張圖可以用幾耐<br />\n幾時先肯影過D新"},{"pid":"5e7c7272f1852c40f8f865594cf1abde32a9d612","tid":2126973,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b980f5c6106c02a39fa751c32e21236f8638526","tid":2126973,"uid":219583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:06:41.000Z","msg":"呢幾張圖可以用幾耐<br />\n幾時先肯影過D新"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:08:39.000Z","msg":"舊先有feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0459a194968b5d9f56f907771fd0b253dc9ce2c4","tid":2126973,"uid":111460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b980f5c6106c02a39fa751c32e21236f8638526","tid":2126973,"uid":219583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:06:41.000Z","msg":"呢幾張圖可以用幾耐<br />\n幾時先肯影過D新"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:09:47.000Z","msg":"我堆物資十年買落擺到依家,無必要轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c148ad213130a4e54165fd5b4b9e2e9d776fd221","tid":2126973,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T06:12:30.000Z","msg":"包裝都改哂啦<img src=\"/assets/